-friendly checkout process, including the option for guest checkout and order tracking.\line Wishlist and Favorites:\line \line Allow users to create wishlists and mark favorite products for easy future reference or sharing.\line Geolocation Services:\line \line Implement geolocation services to show buyers artisans and products in their local area, encouraging support for nearby businesses.\line Notifications and Alerts:\line \line Set up push notifications for users to receive updates on new products, promotions, or events from their favorite artisans.\line Community Events Calendar:\line \line Include a calendar of local artisan events, markets, or fairs to further engage buyers with the artisan community.\line Social Media Integration:\line \line Allow users to share their purchases on social media platforms directly from the app, promoting the local artisan marketplace.\line Remember to prioritize a visually appealing and intuitive user interface for both artisans and buyers. Additionally, consider implementing a robust review and feedback system to maintain a high standard of quality within the marketplace. Regularly update the app to incorporate user feedback and introduce new features that enhance the overall\~ experience}
